00:00:13.210 --> 00:00:14.960
Hello, there.

00:00:14.990 --> 00:00:17.960
Today, I'm going to make 
"Chocolate-Strawberry MOCHI".

00:00:17.990 --> 00:00:23.960
By rolling a MOCHI
make it looks so cute.

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:25.880
The ingredients are here;

00:00:25.910 --> 00:00:32.110
SHIRATAMA-KO (Rice flour), Cake flour, Strawberry,
Sugar and Chocolate.

00:00:32.140 --> 00:00:36.450
I'm going to make a pretty one 
from only the few ingredients.

00:00:36.480 --> 00:00:38.510
So, let's get started.

00:00:38.540 --> 00:00:40.170
So let's get started.

00:00:40.210 --> 00:00:46.120
Add the SHIRATAMA-KO (Rice flour) into a bowl.

00:00:46.150 --> 00:00:51.910
This is 2/5 U.S.cup water.

00:00:51.940 --> 00:00:55.310
Stir the liquid until no lumps remain.

00:00:55.600 --> 00:01:01.470
When the lumps are gone,
add the Cake flour.

00:01:01.500 --> 00:01:06.220
Add the sugar.

00:01:07.880 --> 00:01:11.550
Stir the liquid again.

00:01:12.740 --> 00:01:19.470
Adjust the amount of water as needed,
 and stir the liquid until no lumps remain, like this.

00:01:19.510 --> 00:01:22.130
The dough is done.

00:01:22.170 --> 00:01:24.280
Next,
cook the dough.

00:01:24.310 --> 00:01:26.690
This is a lightly oiled pan.

00:01:26.690 --> 00:01:28.910
Turn on gas.

00:01:29.250 --> 00:01:33.930
When the pan heated,
pour the dough.

00:01:34.210 --> 00:01:39.210
Pour 2 tbsps or so.

00:01:42.630 --> 00:01:48.080
Make the dough in shape of an ellipse, like this.

00:01:50.380 --> 00:01:56.760
When the under side has cooked like this,
flip it.

00:02:04.560 --> 00:02:10.670
It's done when the both sides have cooked.

00:02:13.840 --> 00:02:16.270
And then, the rice cake is done.

00:02:16.310 --> 00:02:19.170
Next,
roll up the dough.

00:02:20.140 --> 00:02:25.130
Put the diced Strawberries.

00:02:27.180 --> 00:02:31.750
Put the Strawberries to stick out from the sides.

00:02:31.780 --> 00:02:35.160
Roll up.

00:02:38.150 --> 00:02:44.700
And then,
insert the Chocolates into the side.

00:02:44.740 --> 00:02:49.740
Insert it on the other side` in the same way.

00:02:49.780 --> 00:02:55.330
Repeat the same step.

00:03:01.100 --> 00:03:05.890
Insert the Chocolates.

00:03:06.930 --> 00:03:13.950
Place them to a serving dish.

00:03:15.540 --> 00:03:20.600
Finally,
arrange a green leaf on the dish.

00:03:21.910 --> 00:03:24.960
And, 
it's ready.

00:03:26.180 --> 00:03:28.800
And there,
my "Chocolate-Strawberry Mochi" is ready to be served.

